                Calculate calories and portion size.
              </li>
              <li
                class="group-hover:opacity-60 hover:translate-x-3 duration-700 hover:!opacity-100 transition-all"
              >
                <i class="text-black fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i>
                Prepare dish from fresh organic and farm products.
